OL,3,CSnowdome in Tamworth to be prosecuted
OL,4,Cfor the death of 12-year-old Louis
OL,5,CWatkiss
OL,7,FThe Snowdome in Tamworth is to be
OL,8,Fprosecuted by the Health and Safety
OL,9,FExecutive (HSE) following the death of
OL,10,FLouis Watkiss.
OL,12,FThe 12-year-old, from Sutton
OL,13,FColdfield, suffered fatal injuries in
OL,14,Fa collision involving a staff member
OL,15,Fat the SnowDome in September 2021.
OL,17,FSince his death, Louis' parents Chris
OL,18,Fand Natalie Watkiss have campaigned to
OL,19,Fmake helmets mandatory for children at
OL,20,Findoor ski slopes.
