OL,7,FLast year, the family released a
OL,8,Ftribute to the 12-year-old boy,
OL,9,Fdescribing him as "our pride, our joy,
OL,10,Four love", telling how they "miss him
OL,11,Fso much it hurts".
OL,13,FIn a statement made today, HSE said:
OL,14,F"After an initial joint investigation
OL,15,Fwith Staffordshire Police, HSE can now
OL,16,Fconfirm Snowdome Limited has been
OL,17,Fcharged with breaching section 3 of
OL,18,FHealth and Safety at Work etc. Act
OL,19,F1974.
